ink": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439156409"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+rTtjafGmf8LEAMaCDU5ODY4MjUzIIHw+f8FMAU4hAFAHHIJNDM5MTU2NDA5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1610530560.2594118", "card_id": "Q_439073939", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 85}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待英国首相称新冠病毒源于人们迷信穿山甲鳞片的疗效？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "彭博社记者向外交部发言人提问：本周一，英国首相约翰逊称新冠病毒源于蝙蝠或穿山甲，源于人们迷信穿山甲鳞片粉末具有滋补效果。他似乎是将新冠疫情归咎于中医药。外交部对此有何评论？ 赵立坚：呵呵（发言人和记者笑）。我们已经多次重申相关立场。新冠病毒溯源是一个科学问题，需要科学家经过细致严谨的研究之后，得出经得起检验的科学结论。没有根据的主观臆测，或者借病毒溯源问题进行炒作，只会对正常的溯源国际合作造成干扰。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e710323cc89705dd1b654e38e53a403a_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "258 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/439073939"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+rTtjafGmf8LEAMaCDU5ODUwMDM4IPGv9v8FMAk4ygFAHXIJNDM5MDczOTM5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1610530560.2598665", "card_id": "Q_438926973", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "怎么看待郑爽退出《追光吧哥哥》后一周左右又回归，称「没协调下来」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-8795ee26a53994b504a5d26dcff55cb9_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "253 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/438926973"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I+rTtjafGmf8LEAMaCDU5ODE3NTk0IN+c8f8FMAI4pAFAHnIJNDM4OTI2OTczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1610530560.2607217", "card_id": "Q_439113658", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 NVIDIA 1 月 13 号发布的 RTX 3060？这次逢 6 有被甜到吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1 月 13 日的 CES 展会上，NVIDIA 正式发布了 RTX 3060 显卡，这是安培游戏显卡的第六位成